Introduction

Han Yu Jin, also known as Yujin, is a South Korean singer originally under Yuehua Entertainment. In 2023, he competed in the hit survival show "Boys Planet," where he ended up ranking 9th place, earning his spot in the group ZEROBASEONE.

He made his official debut with ZEROBASEONE on July 10, 2023, under the management of WAKEONE.
